## Lesson 4: Data Rights 
<img src="https://images.code.org/296fb994c0502d16f96bda2d08e5ba05-image-1724339525656.png" alt="scale icon" width="250px" style="border-radius:10px; float:right; margin: 0 20px 0px 40px;">

#### In this lesson, students will examine and evaluate fundamental data rights. Through a role-playing activity, students will take on the personas of different stakeholders in data rights conversations. 

#### They will attempt to empathize with different positions in order to strengthen their understanding of the nuance inherent in data rights discussions.




